text.textblock: 1. The authority citation for 7 CFR part 993 continues to read as follows:
2. Section 993.128 is amended by revising paragraph (a) to read as follows:
In accordance with the provisions of ยง993.28, the districts referred to therein are described as follows:
The counties of Glenn and Colusa.

That portion of Sutter County north of a line extending along Bogue Road easterly to the Yuba County line and westerly to the Colusa County line and south of a line extending along Clark Road easterly to the Yuba County line and westerly to the Colusa County line.
All of Yolo County and that portion of Sutter County south of a line extending along Bogue Road easterly to the Yuba County line and westerly to the Colusa County line.
The counties of Alpine, Amador, Del Norte, El Dorado, Humboldt, Lake, Lassen, Mendocino, Modoc, Napa, Nevada, Placer, Plumas, Sacramento, Shasta, Sierra, Siskiyou, Sonoma, Tehama and Trinity.
All of Butte County, and that portion of Sutter County north of a line extending along Clark Road easterly to the Yuba County line and westerly to the Colusa County line.
The counties of Fresno, Kings, Merced, San Benito, San Joaquin, Santa Clara, Solano, Tulare and all other counties not included in Districts 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 and 6.
